

passenger --< ticket >-- flight (>-- airline)

Passenger: name, travel balance, (mileage)
- search for flight (origin, destination, date)
- book flight
- add money
- view upcoming trips
- view completed trips 
    Stretch:
    - bookmark flight
    - upgrade ticket

Ticket: passenger, flight, price, class, seat, (stretch: cancellation?, booking date, mileage rewards)
- view ticket info 

Flight: origin, destination, date, duration, (distance)
- view list of passengers
- view flight info (stretch: layovers, total time, etc)

Stretch:
Airline: name
- list of flights
- total revenue on a particular day/month/year
- total revenue from a particular flight




